li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>Elemento HTML&nbsp;<code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> </strong>representa o conteúdo independente, frequentemente com uma legenda&nbsp;(<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a>)<em><code>,</code></em> e é normalmente referido como uma única unidade. Enquanto ela está relacionada com o fluxo principal, sua posição é independente do fluxo principal.Normalmente, isso é uma imagem, uma ilustração, um diagrama, um trecho de código ou uma esquema que é referenciado no texto principal, mas que pode ser movido para outra página ou para um apêndice, sem afetar o fluxo principal.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><em>Notas de uso: </em></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Being a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document#Sectioning_root\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">sectioning root</a>, the outline of the content of the <span style=\"font-family: courier new;\">&lt;figure&gt; </span>element is excluded from the main outline of the document.</li>\n <li>Uma legenda pode ser associada com o elemento <code>&lt;figure&gt;</code>&nbsp;inserindo o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a> &nbsp;dentro dele (no inicio ou no fim).</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Content categories</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document#Sectioning_root\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">sectioning root</a>, palpable content.</li>\n <li><dfn>Permite conteúdo</dfn><dfn>A <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a> element, followed by <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">flow content</a>; or flow content followed by a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a> element; or flow content</dfn>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de TAGs</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn>Permitted parent elements</dfn> Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM interface</dfn> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Este elemento só inclui os</span><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_1","title":"Exemplo 1","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Apenas uma imagem--&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://developer.mozilla.org/static/img/favicon144.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Uma imagem impressionante<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Imagem com legenda --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://developer.mozilla.org/static/img/favicon144.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Uma imagem impressionante<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figcaption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Legenda para a imagem impressionante<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>figcaption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n<figure><img alt=\"MDN Logo\" src=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/static/img/favicon144.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></figure>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n<figure><img alt=\"MDN Logo\" src=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/static/img/favicon144.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n<figcaption>\n<p>Imagem1. MDN Logo</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_2","title":"Example 2","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code>    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figcaption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Obtenha os detalhes do browser usando navigator<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>figcaption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>pre</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          function NavigatorExample(){\n          var txt;\n          txt = \"Browser CodeName: \" + navigator.appCodeName;\n          txt+= \"Browser Name: \" + navigator.appName;\n          txt+= \"Browser Version: \" + navigator.appVersion ;\n          txt+= \"Cookies Enabled: \" + navigator.cookieEnabled;\n          txt+= \"Platform: \" + navigator.platform;\n          txt+= \"User-agent header: \" + navigator.userAgent;\n          }\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>pre</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<figure>\n<figcaption>\n<p>Obtenha os detalhes do browser usando navigator</p>\n</figcaption>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">          function NavigatorExample(){\n          var txt;\n          txt = \"Browser CodeName: \" + navigator.appCodeName;\n          txt+= \"Browser Name: \" + navigator.appName;\n          txt+= \"Browser Version: \" + navigator.appVersion ;\n          txt+= \"Cookies Enabled: \" + navigator.cookieEnabled;\n          txt+= \"Platform: \" + navigator.platform;\n          txt+= \"User-agent header: \" + navigator.userAgent;\n          }\n </pre>\n</figure>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_3","title":"Exemplo 3","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>figcaption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>cite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Edsger Dijkstra :-<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>cite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>figcaption</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\"Se o debugging é o processo de remoção de bugs de software, <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span> então programação deve ser o processo de colocá-los\"<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>figure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<figure>\n<figcaption><cite>Edsger Dijkstra :-</cite></figcaption>\n\n<p>\"Se o debugging é o processo de remoção de bugs de software,&nbsp;<br>\n <span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">então programação deve ser o processo de colocá-los</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\"</span></p>\n</figure>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-figure-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;figure&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/grouping-content.html#the-figure-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;figure&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"navegadores_compatíveis","title":"Navegadores compatíveis","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.10</td>\n   <td>5.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Recurso</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>3.0</td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.0</td>\n   <td>5.1 (iOS 5.0)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja Também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>O <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figcaption\"><code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code></a> elemento.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect4\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Navegadores compatíveis","id":"navegadores_compatíveis"},{"text":"Veja Também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O Elemento HTML <figure> representa o conteúdo independente, frequentemente com uma legenda (<figcaption>), e é normalmente referido como uma única unidade. Enquanto ela está relacionada com o fluxo principal, sua posição é independente do fluxo principal.Normalmente, isso é uma imagem, uma ilustração, um diagrama, um trecho de código ou uma esquema que é referenciado no texto principal, mas que pode ser movido para outra página ou para um apêndice, sem afetar o fluxo principal.","popularity":0.0012,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<figure>: The Figure with Optional Caption element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"figure","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<figure> : l'élément de figure avec légende facultative","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<figure>: キャプションが付けられる図要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<figure>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<figure>: Элемент иллюстрации с необязательной подписью","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<figure>：可附标题内容元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/figure","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/figure/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure","title":"<figure>"}],"pageTitle":"<figure> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}